{"tid":1890393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"銅鑼灣和你 lunch 廿多人持國旗「踩場」推撞 有人受傷送院","createTime":"2020-02-21T07:26:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T07:40:34.000Z","uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"391c4a1378ef128fbb42b80f10e6e600f4d763d4","tid":1890393,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:26:32.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣和你 lunch 廿多人持國旗「踩場」推撞 有人受傷送院<br />\n<br />\n 今日是元朗 721 襲擊七個月，本港多區下午發起「和你lunch」活動，包括銅鑼灣時代廣場等，有 20 多名愛國人士手持國旗「踩場」，有目擊者指兩批人士曾互相推撞以及毆打。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指出，一名男子（圖）嘗試阻止衝突，被便衣警員在混亂期間截停，其腳部受傷包紮，送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n另有兩名人士被帶上警車，有指被捕者是愛國人士，記者暫時未能確認。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/p960x960/87041734_2871911976227737_8244827583150030848_o.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;_nc_ohc=lUWSgM6ZbssAX-1X-7X&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;_nc_tp=6&amp;oh=a8b6c1c55473bd466cc50bc0da3afc40&amp;oe=5EF3A468\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fp960x960%2F87041734_2871911976227737_8244827583150030848_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D111%26_nc_ohc%3DlUWSgM6ZbssAX-1X-7X%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26_nc_tp%3D6%26oh%3Da8b6c1c55473bd466cc50bc0da3afc40%26oe%3D5EF3A468&h=8990a460&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c793812d35571cd162c76408932df3cdd13ad96","tid":1890393,"uid":68689,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:29:27.000Z","msg":"愛國就去武漢幫手啦 fing支旗仔把撚咩"},{"pid":"6d049625727ca0c4153c687529f7e52251cdee2a","tid":1890393,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:29:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />送入集中營啦"},{"pid":"f0fdb311bb7ec7352017bf88b6e2e111dae67d44","tid":1890393,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:32:54.000Z","msg":"比popo拉 老閪都認係藍絲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb5a161d18c0b34f6812364e70981daa40f04eed","tid":1890393,"uid":3